<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>SINGLE REDUCTION, TANDEM AXLES: SPICER J400-S, W460-S - INSTALL</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcsubsec>
        <title>INSTALL</title>
        <svcproc svcproctype="install" graphiccount="3">
            <title>INTER-AXLE DIFFERENTIAL</title>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Apply 1/8 inch bead of RTV gasket material onto mounting surface (
                    <hotlnk xrefid="f14004b6">Figure 116</hotlnk>). Install inter-axle differential assembly into
                    intermediate case. Install cover bolts. Be sure to install the one longer bolt in the correct
                    position. Tighten bolts to 75 to 90 ft-lbs. (102 to 122 Nm).
                </para>
                <figure id="f14004b6" figsize="col-wide">
                    <graphic id="g14004b6" filename="../figg14/G14004B6.webp" type="webp"/>
                    <caption>Figure 115. Apply RTV Gasket Material onto Mounting Surface</caption>
                </figure>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Apply 1/8 inch bead of RTV gasket material onto mounting surface next to cylinder as
                    shown in
                    <hotlnk xrefid="f14004b7">Figure 117</hotlnk>, and install onto intermediate case.
                </para>
                <figure id="f14004b7" figsize="col-wide">
                    <graphic id="g14004b7" filename="../figg14/G14004B7.webp" type="webp"/>
                    <caption>Figure 116. Apply RTV Gasket Material onto Mounting Surface</caption>
                </figure>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Tighten mounting bolts to 30 to 40 ft-lbs. (41 to 54 Nm) (
                    <hotlnk xrefid="f14004b8">Figure 118</hotlnk>
                </para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">As a check, connect air line to power divider control to be certain it is operable.
                    There should be a distinct clunk sound when air is applied.
                </para>
                <figure id="f14004b8" figsize="col-wide">
                    <graphic id="g14004b8" filename="../figg14/G14004B8.webp" type="webp"/>
                    <caption>Figure 117. Tighten Mounting Bolts</caption>
                </figure>
            </step1>
        </svcproc>
    </svcsubsec>
